This method is the most promising and economical. The concept of catalytic converter comes under this category. The converter is placed before the silencer without appreciable change in engine design that can convert harmful gases into non-polluted ones using a catalyst concept (Kalam et al. 2009); fo example, the lean mixture of CO and CH4 in the vehicle exhaust can be catalytically converted into CO2 and H2O vapor and released in the atmosphere (Eqs. 3 and 4).3CO+0.5O2→CO2−∆Hr=−393.5kJmol−1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
